sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Unregistered User
    participant FE as React<br/>JoinEnvironmentPage
    participant API as DRF<br/>JoinEnvironmentView
    participant SER as JoinEnvironmentSerializer
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>FE: Enter invitation PIN
    FE->>API: POST /api/environments/join/
    API->>SER: JoinEnvironmentSerializer.validate(data)
    SER->>DB: Environment.objects.get(pin=pin)
    DB-->>SER: Environment instance (or 404)
    SER-->>API: Validated environment
    API->>DB: EnvironmentMembership.objects.create(user, env, role="member")
    DB-->>API: Membership created
    API-->>FE: 200 OK {env_id, env_name, role}
    FE-->>U: Redirect to environment dashboard
